\id RUT Matupi Chin Standard Bible (MCSB) 
\h RUTH 
\toc1 RUTH 
\toc2 Ruth 
\toc3 Rut 
\mt1 RUTH  
\mt4 (The Book of Ruth)  
\is1 Ruth Cabu Kawng  
\im Laitloekkung rhoek neh Israel manghai rhoek a om tom vaengkah ni. Ruth kawng cil ol a toi ca bawt a daek. Bethlehem kah cako pakhat te khokha dongah khothoeng kah Moab ram la a poenngnah kawng a thui. Kho a sak li vaengah a ca rhoi loh Moab nu a yunah rhoi. Kum rha tluk a om vaengah a ca rhoi neh a va khaw duek tih Naomi te nuhmai la om. Te vaengah Bethlehem ah khobuh coeng tila a yaak dongah mael hamla cai. A langa rhoi loh a vai dae Moab ah khosa rhoi mai a ti nah. Te vaengah Orpah loh a ngai tih Ruth tah Judah ram la cet ham altha. Ruth he bahoeng khuel tih a hnukah tah Boaz loh a yunah. Ruth he Moab hoel la om dae Jew hlang a vanah rhang neh a casak lamloh manghai David he thoeng. Ruth dongah he yan Palestine ram kah lotawn cangah kawng khaw, manuca neh nuhmai cadah ham khokhan kawng khaw a thui. \k Ruth Cabu \k* he \sc b c \sc* 400 tluk vaengah daek coini tila poeknah om.  
\iot Sawt Yoeinah  
\io1 Ruth loh Moaba caehtak \ior 1. 1-22\ior*  
\io1 Ruth Bethlehem kah khosaknah \ior 2. 1—4. 22\ior*  
\c 1  
\s1 Naomi Cako Moab La Poeng Uh  
\p
